OL,3,CEverything you need to know about the
OL,4,Cbizarre sport - Cornish Hurling
OL,6,FITV News' Charlotte Gay went along to
OL,7,Fthe Shrove Tuesday game of Hurling in
OL,8,FSt Columb.
OL,10,FThere are many unusual traditions that
OL,11,Fhave lived on for centuries in
OL,12,FCornwall and perhaps the game of
OL,13,F"Hurling the Silverball" is one of the
OL,14,Fstrangest.
OL,16,FThe ancient sport used to be played in
OL,17,Ftowns and villages across the
OL,18,Fpeninsular but just two towns are
OL,19,Fknown to continue to play the game.
OL,20,FOne onand more recently on Shrove
OL,21,FTuesday in St Columb.
