OL,3,CEverything you need to know about the
OL,4,Cbizarre sport - Cornish Hurling
OL,6,FThere are variations on the rules
OL,7,Fbetween the towns but for the adults
OL,8,Fgame in mid Cornwall two teams, town
OL,9,Fversus country, compete to carry the
OL,10,Fball over the parish boundary a mile
OL,11,Faway from the start.
OL,13,FColin Rescorla is the third generation
OL,14,Fto make the silver ball needed for the
OL,15,Fgame. He says there is "considerable
OL,16,Fglory" in winning the ball and
OL,17,Foutsiders are in "total disbelief" at
OL,18,Fthe chaos of the rough game.
