OL,3,CEverything you need to know about the
OL,4,Cbizarre sport - Cornish Hurling
OL,6,F"There are no rules other than you
OL,7,Fdon't ride on a vehicle and if you are
OL,8,Ftold to give up the ball you do."
OL,10,FThe ball is made from a core of
OL,11,Fapplewood and covered by two sides of
OL,12,Fsilver with the words "TOWN AND
OL,13,FCOUNTRY DO YOUR BEST" engraved on the
OL,14,Fcentre band.
OL,16,FColin has noticed more players want to
OL,17,Fkeep their winning ball but it comes
OL,18,Fwith a four figure price-tag.
