OL,3,CEverything you need to know about the
OL,4,Cbizarre sport - Cornish Hurling
OL,6,FDescribing the game as a "real brawl"
OL,7,FJeremy says it is 'it's tougher than a
OL,8,Fgame of rugby."
OL,10,F"People do get hurt occasionally using
OL,11,Fa few black eyes, bloody noses, black
OL,12,Feyes and a few limp away, deciding not
OL,13,Fto continue with (the game)."
OL,15,FBen Lomax won the ball last year for
OL,16,FTeam Country.
OL,18,FHe thinks it's getting "tamer" but
OL,19,Fadmits that's not how it looks to
OL,20,Foutsiders.
